{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"f2b11e32-39bd-5693-9f12-4e93a61213f2","frontmatter":{"title":"Ubuntu 下 LAMP环境搭建","date":"2015/08/24","tags":["Ubuntu","PHP"],"issueId":2},"fields":{"slug":"/posts/201508242"},"excerpt":"安装 安装apache2 安装php模块 安装Mysql 安装其他模块 测试Apache 浏览器访问  http://localhost/ 页面显示It Works！即为Apache服务器成功安装运行 修改权限 安装phpmyadmin 安装过程选择apache2,输入密码。 …","html":"<h2 id=\"安装\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\" aria-label=\"安装 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>安装</h2>\n<h3 id=\"安装apache2\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85apache2\" aria-label=\"安装apache2 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>安装apache2</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ sudo apt-get install apache2</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"安装php模块\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85php%E6%A8%A1%E5%9D%97\" aria-label=\"安装php模块 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>安装php模块</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ sudo apt-get install php5</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"安装Mysql\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Mysql\" aria-label=\"安装Mysql permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>安装Mysql</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ sudo apt-get install mysql-server\n$ sudo apt-get install mysql-client</code></pre></div>\n<!--more-->\n<h3 id=\"安装其他模块\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E6%A8%A1%E5%9D%97\" aria-label=\"安装其他模块 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>安装其他模块</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ sudo apt-get install libapache2-mod-php5\n$ sudo apt-get install libapache2-mod-auth-mysql\n$ sudo apt-get install php5-mysql\n$ sudo apt-get install php5-gd</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"测试Apache\"><a href=\"#%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95Apache\" aria-label=\"测试Apache permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>测试Apache</h3>\n<p>浏览器访问 <a href=\"http://localhost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">http://localhost/</a></p>\n<p>页面显示It Works！即为Apache服务器成功安装运行</p>\n<h3 id=\"修改权限\"><a href=\"#%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E6%9D%83%E9%99%90\" aria-label=\"修改权限 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>修改权限</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ sudo chmod 777 /var/www/html</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"安装phpmyadmin\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85phpmyadmin\" aria-label=\"安装phpmyadmin permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>安装phpmyadmin</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ sudo apt-get install phpmyadmin</code></pre></div>\n<p>安装过程选择apache2,输入密码。</p>\n<h3 id=\"测试phpmyadmin\"><a href=\"#%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95phpmyadmin\" aria-label=\"测试phpmyadmin permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>测试phpmyadmin</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ sudo ln -s /usr/share/phpmyadmin /var/www/html</code></pre></div>\n<p>浏览器访问 <a href=\"http://localhost/phpmyadmin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">http://localhost/phpmyadmin</a>,并登录。</p>\n<h2 id=\"配置\"><a href=\"#%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE\" aria-label=\"配置 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>配置</h2>\n<h3 id=\"启用mod_rewrite模块\"><a href=\"#%E5%90%AF%E7%94%A8mod_rewrite%E6%A8%A1%E5%9D%97\" aria-label=\"启用mod_rewrite模块 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>启用mod_rewrite模块</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ sudo a2enmod rewrite</code></pre></div>\n<p>启用后重启Apache服务器：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ sudo service apache2 restart</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"设置Apache支持-htm-html-php\"><a href=\"#%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AEApache%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81-htm-html-php\" aria-label=\"设置Apache支持 htm html php permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>设置Apache支持 .htm .html .php</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ sudo gedit /etc/apache2/apache2.conf&amp;</code></pre></div>\n<p>打开并添加：<code class=\"language-text\">AddType application/x-httpd-php .htm .html .php</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"测试PHP网页\"><a href=\"#%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95PHP%E7%BD%91%E9%A1%B5\" aria-label=\"测试PHP网页 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>测试PHP网页</h3>\n<p>在/var/www/html下新建mysql_test.php:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"php\"><pre class=\"language-php\"><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token php language-php\"><span class=\"token delimiter important\">&lt;?php</span>\n<span class=\"token variable\">$link</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">mysql_connect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token double-quoted-string string\">\"localhost\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token double-quoted-string string\">\"root\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token double-quoted-string string\">\"password\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token variable\">$link</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">die</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">'Could not connect: '</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span> <span class=\"token function\">mysql_error</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">else</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">echo</span> <span class=\"token double-quoted-string string\">\"Mysql 配置正确!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">mysql_close</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$link</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token delimiter important\">?></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>访问 <a href=\"http://localhost/mysql_test.php\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">http://localhost/mysql_test.php</a>，显示“Mysql配置正确”即完成</p>","timeToRead":2}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"f2b11e32-39bd-5693-9f12-4e93a61213f2","redirect":true,"redirectUrl":"/posts/201508242"}}